    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You focus Chakra into your salivary glands, producing a large amount of saliva and hardening it to a mud-like consistency which you spit at the target, making a ranged attack roll which deals 1d4 water damage on hit. Alternatively, you can target small fires such as torches or candles, and extinguish them if you hit.<br><br>If you know the Toushou technique, you may perform both Toushou and this technique in quick succession as a Full-round action. Doing so has the standard effects of Toushou, and changes the damage of this technique to 1d4+2 (half cold, half water), cannot put out small fires, but may break fragile objects.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to fire an additional sphere (up to 1 sphere per 2 levels total). Each sphere can affect the same target, or a different one.</p>\n\n",
